page.title: 11JOBS
page.content: MR.TYLER WORKS AS A SHEPHARD ON TOWNSEND FARM. IN HIS SPARE TIME HE DOES CARVING.MRS.TYLER IS A HOUSE WIFE.MR.BRANDON IS A LORRY DRIVER OR A CARTER.MRS.BRANDON HAS A PART TIME JOB AT A PLAYSCHOOL, SHE IS ALSO A HOUSE WIFE. MR.GWILLIAM DOES WELDING,HE WELDS TRICYCLES.MRS.GWILLIAM DOES HOUSE WORK, AND BAR WORK.MRS.WARGENT DOES READING AND SEWING IN HER SPARE TIME, SHE WORKS AT THE POSTOFFICE.MR COKER IS A COMPUTER ENGINEER.MRS COKER IS A BUSINESS ADMINISTRATOR.MR BOWEN RUNS A BUSINESS.MRS BOWEN IS A HOUSE WIFE.MR PLUMLEY IS THE VET . MR WELLS IS A CRAFTSMAN IN WOOD.MR RICKETTS IS THE VICAR OF BRAMPTON ABBOTTS.MRS WINNEY IS A HOUSE WIFE. MR WINNEY IS A CONTRACTOR FOR BUILDING FIRMS.MRS.MARSHALL IS A HOUSE WIFE AND MOTHER.MR.MARSHALL WORKS AT AN ESTATE AGENTS.{ By Maria Tingle
